{ GPT partition table #gpt-partition-table

  { Begin on harddisk

    The GPT parition table starts at position 512 on a harddisk and is identified with the first 8 bytes being `EFI PART`:
code {
# → Linux/shell/commands/dd if=/dev/nvme0n1 status=none bs=1 count=8 skip=512 ; echo
EFI PART
code }

  }
}
